Name: Loft Style Industrial Design Handmade Iron Bed - Model Pandora | Creates A Unique Bedroom Decor
Description: Find a unique industrial handmade iron bed . Lifetime Guarantee, Eco-friendly & safe. Handmade metal beds made by Volcano, Greece. Shipping worldwide ...In industrial style to create a unique bedroom decor. It is made of wrought iron with rebar steel rods "Lifetime Guarantee" The guarantee covers the welds & the stability of the structure of the bed. Assembly time: only 15 minutes (The product accompanied by detailed instructions with images). The bed can be constructed only in 1 type: 1. Bed without Footboard (NO-FTB) All beds include Anatomic Frame (mattress base) with 11 wood boards, providing maximum strength & stability to the bed. It can be manufactured in any dimension & color you choose from the list above. Tip For a better aesthetic result, the bed should be in a colour contrasting the wall, to emphasize its design. The paintjobs are done with acrylic powder paints & cured in a special oven at 200c. This results in the perfect adhesion of the paint onto the metal, ensuring longer durability over time. If you choose color with patina, we inform you that it's applied exclusively to the design of the bed & not to the side parts & the base of the bed. All materials used in the production of the products are recyclable. IMPORTANT VOLCANO products are subjected to a special demagnetization treatment using the Curie method (raising the temperature of the metal above the 770C) & are absolutely safe for your health. All VOLCANO products are signed by the manufacturer with an embossed metal signature on the side of the foot. Volcano, stablished in 1976 & situated in Thessaloniki, Greece, is one of the best-known companies in Europe in the wrought iron furniture field. External bed dimensions: Bed width same as the mattress size Length for bed without footboard: +10cm from mattress length Headboard Height: 118 cm ( 111cm ) Bed Base Height: 32cm There may be fluctuations on dimensions headboard & footboard where the width & length of the bed increases some extra centimeters compared with the bed base size due to the peculiarity of the design. Name: Wall Shelves For Bedroom, Floating Nightstand, Bedside Shelf, Shelf Above Bed, Bedroom
Description: Our beautiful wall shelves for a bedroom are the perfect floating bedside shelf, floating shelf above for your bed, or shelves for anywhere in your bedroom. Each item is meticulously handcrafted using organically sourced lumber, which looks perfect in modern, contemporary, rustic, or Scandinavian décor. You'll love the beautiful grain throughout, creating a warm & inviting atmosphere to work on. You'll love seeing the beautiful grain permeate through the wood, showcasing the work mother nature slowly did over time. It's an heirloom piece that you'll have in your home for years to come. We handcraft everything from scratch, in some cases drying the wood ourselves to be sure of its quality before it makes it into your home. We're a team of woodworkers that are passionate about creating bespoke furniture that is made to your specifications. We only use high end finishes & brackets, because we believe in quality. Our shelf is finished with a 0% VOC plant-based finish, so you'll feel good about putting this piece in your home. Sizing: The shelf is made from lumber that is between 1.5-2" thick. You can select various widths & lengths up to 96". If you need a custom size, purchase the size larger than it & comment your specific size in the personalization box. Shipping: We aim to get the item out within 1-2 weeks. Shipping can take up to an additional 7 days. Installation: All of our floating shelf brackets must be installed into a solid surface such as a stud, masonry (concrete/brick), or otherwise solid surface. Incorrect mounting could result in a sagging shelf or one that cannot support the weight. A drill, level, tape measure, & screws will be required for installation. Ordering: Simply select your size, & quantity we'll then get to work on your piece. If you have any questions or specific requests, please reach out to us. About Us: We're a family owned business that's passionate about woodworking, & creating heirloom-quality furniture. We're located in the former lumber capital of the world, Williamsport, PA, & are striving to revive this once booming industry one table at a time. All of the items are made on the site of a former 1800s lumber mill, once called Brick Mill where we got our name. We know you'll love your item & will work to make sure you're completely satisfied with your purchase. Description: Hematite Rutile Smoky Quartz Bed with Points & babies or companions, 56 grams & 2" long, this piece is amazing. I keep seeing boxes of gold rutile hematite go for crazy sums so I never purchased any for my shop. But someone sold me this piece for my shop & I wish you'd look at the gold rutiles at the bottom of the formation - there's even a single gold bar floating between some of the smoky quartz on the edge. I don't often get my mind blown but today has been a day that really unique crystals found their way to me. I can't believe this formation grew with rutile & hematite at its base. & 56 grams! Name: Last Name & Established Date Sign | With Quote Inspirations Signs Above Bed Decor Anniversary Gift Wedding
Description: Each sign is handmade from solid Pine wood We use Chalk paint on all of our lettering to get that vintage/farmhouse look. We use a high quality oil based stain for our frames. We use a Flat ultra white interior paint for the white background on all of our boards.Our signs are NOT made with vinyl lettering, & we DO NOT use canvas or thin material for the construction of our products. Our signs are not made by mass production, when you order a sign & it is made JUST FOR YOU. Every sign is hand painted & hand made for each individual order. Each sign will significantly resemble one another, while having its own characteristic due to the knots, wood grain & slight variations of each piece of hand cut wood. We do not try to cover up, change, or get rid of any of these characteristics, we feel this is what makes the sign unique. We lightly distress the frames to add to the rustic/ farmhouse look & will include small imperfections which adds to the rustic character of your sign. Our items are made from cut pine, & put together with wood glue & high quality nails. When ordering signs, please be aware that the size could be 1'' larger or smaller. So if you order a 50'' sign, it could be slightly longer 51" or an inch shorter 49". This happens during the inspection of our boards, we do this in the interest of our customers to ensure your getting a clean, gorgeous piece of wood. (Due to knots & imperfections) These signs are made to be used indoors, but can be placed outdoors although they will age, fade & may warp outdoors. Name: Antique Copper Bed Warmer Or Warming Pan 38 " Star On Lid
Description: This is a Antique Copper Bed Warmer or Warming Pan with a Star design on the Lid. It measures approx. 38 inches long. The handle is wood & it has been turned. There is a hole in the end of the wood handle where a little metal loop used to be so it could be hung on the wall, but it is missing. These were made from the 1500's to the late 1800's. Guess they finally figured out the putting embers in them to warm a bed up was not so safe to breathe & also caused fires. Glad we do not have to use them anymore. It is in good condition with normal age wear. I will let the buyer clean it if they want to shine the copper up...I do not like to alter antiques & collectibles. This would really look great hanging by a Fireplace for the Farmhouse look. I ship to the USA. No International shipping. I also insure all of my packages to the USA to make sure that they arrive to you safely. Any questions, please ask before purchasing. Thanks for looking. Description: A modern, different, & up-to-date style for every home with my mandala bedding. Bringing creativity & harmony to you with the balancing designs of mandala bedding. My mandala bedding sets will bring you harmony, as they are uniquely designed to guarantee you will not meet elsewhere & will be different from it. Also, the mandala bedding sets are made of incredible quality materials that will provide you with a full & relaxed dream filled with warmth. My mandala bedding sets are made of high-quality organic cotton sateen & very soft microfiber designed for bedding sets. The cotton sateen is distinguished by its matte surface & radiant appearance. Due to a large number of threads & specially woven fibers, cotton satin has exceptional strength, softness, & durability over time. The material is designed for good & complete sleep provides good air circulation & absorbs the maximum excess moisture released by the skin during sleep. The design is printed on soft microfiber fabric designed specifically for mandala bedding sets. Microfiber is composed of extremely fine textile fibers twice as fine as silk. It is characterized by exceptional strength & has a smooth & soft surface. Microfiber absorbs moisture & allows the body to breathe by regulating heat. Name: As For Me & My House We Will Serve The Lord | Living Room Sign Framed Signs With Quote Above Bed
Description: Each sign is handmade from solid Pine wood We use Chalk paint on all of our lettering to get that vintage/farmhouse look. We use a high quality oil based stain for our frames. We use a Flat ultra white interior paint for the white background on all of our boards.Our signs are NOT made with vinyl lettering, & we DO NOT use canvas or thin material for the construction of our products. Our signs are not made by mass production, when you order a sign & it is made JUST FOR YOU. Every sign is hand painted & hand made for each individual order. Each sign will significantly resemble one another, while having its own characteristic due to the knots, wood grain & slight variations of each piece of hand cut wood. We do not try to cover up, change, or get rid of any of these characteristics, we feel this is what makes the sign unique. We lightly distress the frames to add to the rustic/ farmhouse look & will include small imperfections which adds to the rustic character of your sign. Our items are made from cut pine, & put together with wood glue & high quality nails. When ordering signs, please be aware that the size could be 1'' larger or smaller. So if you order a 50'' sign, it could be slightly longer 51" or an inch shorter 49". This happens during the inspection of our boards, we do this in the interest of our customers to ensure your getting a clean, gorgeous piece of wood. (Due to knots & imperfections) These signs are made to be used indoors, but can be placed outdoors although they will age, fade & may warp outdoors. TIPS FOR SIGN SIZES: 13x48 is recommended for the queen & king beds 13x38 is great for nursery twins & full size ✅See stain choices in pictures, If you would like to request a different color background please send me a message. ✅Hangers are added to back ✅How to Order: Please specify colors in the drop down menu. This happens during the inspection of our boards, we do this in the interest of our customers to ensure your getting a clean, gorgeous piece of wood. Description:
Dee Zee Bed Mats are a cost-effective solution to protect your truck bed surface free from scratches, dings and dents. Shifting cargo is also a detriment to your truck's appearance. Bed Mats help prevent shifting cargo from damaging your truck and eliminate chasing down loose items strewn about the truck bed.
Dee Zee Bed Mats are custom fitting to your truck by contouring around wheel wells for ultimate coverage. Rubber cleats on the reverse side facilitate water drainage and keep the Bed Mat securely in place. you can trust heavy-duty Dee Zee Bed Mats to last the life of your truck.
Each heavy-duty Dee Zee Bed Mat is constructed from 0.375 in. (9.52mm) high-density Rubber compound that is resistant to gas or oil spills. The tightly compressed Rubber fibers are abrasion and tear resistant from your cargo. Your custom fit Bed Mat will not crack, rust or break in extreme temperatures. Resilient Rubber compound material deflects harmful UV rays to decrease fading.

Name: 14 in. Universal Metal Platform Bed Frame for No Box Spring Needed with Steel Slat Support & Quick Lock Functionality, Black - Full Size
Description:
Refresh the look of your bedroom or guest room with this black textured finish full metal platform bed frame that can be used with most headboards or as a standalone bedframe. The lack of a headboard and footboard will streamline a modern bedroom but will also give the illusion of an open, airy space in a small room and making the bed is infinitely easier with no obstacles in the way. If you like to change the layout of your room often, this metal full bed frame is easily moved making redecorating a breeze. Best of all, the 12.5 inches of clearance under the frame allows for generous underbed storage and easy access for cleaning. If you're looking for a solid, stable metal bed frame that can last for years without breaking down you've come to the right place. This platform bed frame is constructed from 19 gauge solid steel reinforced with metal screw construction and holds up to 650 pounds to accommodate most users. Solid steel slats stay in place to prevent sagging helping to increase the lifetime of your mattress. This metal platform bed frame will support your memory foam, latex or traditional innerspring mattress with no need for a box spring. Felt pads between the middle rail and support slats reduce noise for a peaceful nights sleep while adhesive strips prevent your mattress from moving. Fixed plastic floor glides will prevent damage to your flooring. In case of spills or dust build up, simply clean with a damp cloth. Easily assembled, this full size metal platform bed frame will be ready to go in 30 minutes or less with the included tools for quick use. Pair this metal frame with our 12 Inch CertiPur-US Certified Foam and Pocket Spring Mattress to complete your setup and get an excellent nights sleep.

Name: R12022LGPJ 5.8 ft. Painted Hard Truck Bed Cover, GPJ Glory Red Pearl for 2019-2020 GM Sierra
Description:
The ARE Fusion Tonneau Cover combines the custom look of a painted truck bed cover with the functionality of a hard folding cover. Constructed from heavy duty aluminum panels that are highly dent resistant to keep your cover looking great. ARE adds a convenient battery operated LED light along with durable carpeted paneling underneath, completing that custom look. The Fusion can be operated from either side of the truck bed by pulling the release cable to disengage the slam latches. When closing the cover, the slam latches will automatically lock the cover to the rails. A universal tailgate seal helps prevent water from seeping in while allowing you to open and close the tailgate with the cover closed. Full bed access is possible in seconds with the Fusion truck bed cover. Release the slam latches and fold the cover, panel by panel, towards the cab for partial bed access. Full bed access is achieved by lifting the cover towards the cab and attaching the support arms to securely drive down the road with the cover up. The Fusion has L-rails that mount to the bed caps with clamp-on brackets, providing a no-drill installation. For weather protection, interior and exterior seals help to keep most of the elements out. The provided drain tubes work with the mounting rails like gutters to help flush out excess water to keep your cargo dry. Drilling may be needed if your truck does not have factory drain holes.
FeaturesFits 2019-2020 GM Sierra 5 '8inches bed 1500 w / or w / out Multipro Tailgate Paint Code: GPJ Glory Red Pearl
Aluminum panels are painted-to-match your truck's color code
Exterior and interior seals help deflect elements from entering your bed and the integrated drain track helps push any water to the front and out of bed
Open your tailgate with the cover in the opened or closed position
Cover can be propped open with integrated support arms, allowing you to drive with the cover in the fully opened position
Made in the USA
Compatibility:2019-2020 GM Sierra

Name: 86793 Heavyweight Bed Mats 97.25 X 64 In.
Description:
Dee Zee Bed Mats are a cost-effective solution to protect your truck bed surface free from scratches, dings and dents. Shifting cargo is also a detriment to your truck's appearance. Bed Mats help prevent shifting cargo from damaging your truck and eliminate chasing down loose items strewn about the truck bed.
Dee Zee Bed Mats are custom fitting to your truck by contouring around wheel wells for ultimate coverage. Rubber cleats on the reverse side facilitate water drainage and keep the Bed Mat securely in place. you can trust heavy-duty Dee Zee Bed Mats to last the life of your truck.
Each heavy-duty Dee Zee Bed Mat is constructed from 0.375 in. (9.52mm) high-density Rubber compound that is resistant to gas or oil spills. The tightly compressed Rubber fibers are abrasion and tear resistant from your cargo. Your custom fit Bed Mat will not crack, rust or break in extreme temperatures. Resilient Rubber compound material deflects harmful UV rays to decrease fading.

When it comes to hauling a load from one work site to the other, from home to the campground or just from your buddy's old place to the new, your truck can handle it. But when intemperate weather and hazardous roads threaten whatever you've got back there, the Pace Edwards UltraGroove Metal Tonneau Cover is what you need to keep the storms of life at bay. Boasting an aerodynamic, metallic design that's double-tough thank the matte-black, heavy-gauge aluminum construction for that this retractable replacement tonneau is as functional as they come. Withdrawing easily into the canister head at the front of your truck bed at the simple turn of a lock knob, the Pace Edwards UltraGroove Metal Truck Bed Cover secures every foot along the rail for as much accessibility as you need. To close, just give a tug on the integrated pull strap. This bad boy's been outfitted with drain tubes at the front and rear of the rail to facilitate water runoff on monsoon-y days and nights.
Features88-13 Chevrolet/GMC Silverado/Sierra 8' bed
Aluminum construction
Matte black finish
Easy retractable operation
No drill installation brackets
Intermittent locking
Weather resistant design
Compatibility:1988-2013 Chevy & Gmc C & K & Silverado Heavy Duty & 2014 Hd
SpecificationsFitment: Direct Fit
Country of Origin: USA
Weight: 137 lbs
